properties.property:
The leader of the new dangerous cult is called the Yellow Father. He is persuasive and erudite; not many can resist his influence.
His current location is unknown. Somewhere in the galaxy, he keeps training new acolytes.
His teachings are like an untreatable malignant brain tumor: they can only be cured by blowing the head off.
Fortunately, this memetic disease spreads only through direct transmission. The only way to get infected is to personally acquire the teachings from someone already initiated.
Therefore, when you meet the messengers, shoot before you ask any questions.
